<#if msg.locations?has_content>

</#if>.
</@line>

<@line>
Work is carried out by ${params['Vessel'].value['Vessel Name'].value} 
<#if (params['Vessel'].value['Vessel Call Sign'].value)??>
 call sign ${params['Vessel'].value['Vessel Call Sign'].value}
</#if>.
<#if (params['Guard Vessel'].value)??>
  Guard vessels will be in the area. The vessels are listening on VHF channel 16
<#else>
  The vessel is listening on VHF channel 16
</#if> 
<#if (params['Vessel'].value['VHF Channel'].value)??>
 and ${params['Vessel'].value['VHF Channel'].value}
</#if>.
</@line>

<@line>

<#if (params['Min Dist'].value)??>

</#if>.
</@line>

<#if msg.locations?has_content>

</#if>.
<#if (params['Depth (m)'].value)??>
 The depth above the wreck is ${params['Depth (m)'].value}m.
</#if>

The wreck has been marked with 
<#list params['Marking'].values as mark>
    ${mark['AtoN type'].longValue}
    <#if (mark['Light'].value)??> 
       showing ${lightFormatter.format(mark['Light'].value)}
    </#if>
    <#if (mark['Distance'].value)??> 
       approx. ${mark['Distance'].value}m
       <#if (mark['Bearing'].longValue)??> 
          ${mark['Bearing'].longValue}
       </#if>
       of the position
    </#if>
    <#if mark_has_next>, ${text('and')} </#if>
</#list>.
</@line>

<@line>

</@line>
